You need to give every Citizen Internet Connectivity. The best Internet. Your Internet!

You start with $2.000
Every radio tower costs $1.000
Every small house which gets internet brings you $50
Every big House which gets internet brings you $100
A simple internet tower has a round coverage of 5 tiles

Every tower costs $100 maintenance per 10 seconds

The game is over when you have no money left

Your goal is to reach a coverage of at least 80% of houses
